===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|かばね|alt=尸:mainly&#32;in&#32;compounds}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=かばね|-}}.  Found in the ''{{w|Man'yōshū}}'', completed some time after 759 {{CE}},<ref>{{RQ:Manyoshu|18|4094}}, text [https://web.archive.org/web/20230830001229/http://jti.lib.virginia.edu/japanese/manyoshu/Man18Yo.html#4094 here]</ref> and also cited to the ''{{w|Nihon Shoki}}'' of 720 {{CE}}.<ref name="KDJ"/>

Appears to be a compound.  Ultimate derivation {{unk|ja|sort=かばね|nocap=1}}.

